1. **Animated Transitions**
   ```css
   /* Add to global CSS */
   .screen-transition {
     animation: pixelReveal 1.5s ease;
   }
   
   @keyframes pixelReveal {
     0% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 0, 0 0); }
     100% { clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%); }
   }
   ```

2. **Signature Sound Design**
   ```javascript
   // Western-themed audio feedback
   playSound('spur_jingle.wav') // On successful actions
   playSound('tumbleweed_pass.wav') // During loading
   ```

3. **Consistent Western Typography**
   ```css
   /* Import and apply */
   @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Western&display=swap');
   
   body {
     font-family: 'Western', 'Courier New', monospace;
   }
   ```
